title: Good over-engage champion
body:
I have been playing lol for about 1 year now and have been buying lots of champions to suit my needs, but I over-engage a lot whilst playing.
can anyone tell me a good over-engageable champion
thanks

replies.body: Alistar is the biggest sack of meat ever and he can do some dumb stuff and still live
30-40% cdr amumu built mostly tank might be quite troublesome at lvl 18 a lot of q spam, etc..
